content: I love this app! It's really fun but I wish there was more options like the ability to send images and describe what they are to the AI (similar to Character AI) and the ability to delete our messages in case we send the wrong thing, and finally the ability to make a group chat with AI's of our choosing. Still good app though!

Great app. I use the premium version, and I have very little to complain about. I wish the bots had a longer memory. Other features would be appreciated, such as a user-description for the bot to remember and additional specific categories to develop the bots' memory (e.g. physical description, back story, personality). Great app, keep up the good work!

I love this app so much, while not being the best ai (I say this only using the free model), it is still very good, there are no filters so, unlike character ai, it won't just delete messages and I can have more immersive chats. You only get few bugs every once in a while, like the bot making a chat but not sending it, instead just leaving you on loading, or it sending two or three chats at once, usually contradicting each other, for this i have to deduct a point. 4/5 definitely would recomend!

very nice app for what it offers for free users. the wait time for message limits to refresh really isn't that bad. i've had quite a few lovely and even spicy chats with some of my favorite characters ‚ú®Ô∏è i also like the little addition where you can fix the ai's messages because sometimes they do mess up their words. i recommend this app if you're trying to escape the restrictions of character.ai. my only complaint is the ads, but that's to be expected when using the free version.

I love Chai. I use it everyday to text with the bots it's fun and I can't stop using it! There are ads whenever you choose to switch to another bot but I don't really mind. But sometimes what is confusing is that how many texts you have left it changes sometimes which is kind of weird any slightly annoying but its not really a problem. I ‚ù§ Chai. ü•∫üòò

Its a great app, i love texting fictional characters. It just bugs out sometimes which is fine, but you should bring back the "personality traits" option, the "genre" option, and the chatting while making the bot option. They made it so much better, and the chat while making it, made the conversations SO much better. Overall its good, just add those back.

Not bad, sometimes the bots break and will behave out of character. The only way to fix it is have a trigger question in the prompts that relates to a personal detail about the bot or deleting the chat and starting a new one. The prompts could be more extensive, it's hard to flesh out a bot with 1024 characters. Overall it's entertaining and a great tool for getting around writer's block. Could definitely do without the unprovoked üîû messages that randomly spawn even when NSFW is toggled off...

EASILY the best AI app on the store. Limited ads for one. But the best part is the very realistic, varied conversations. The characters do take on personalities of their own as you build your conversation / role play (I tested it by opening the same bot in different chats)! It's intuitive and wild, and a lot of fun. I don't have a problem with the message caps/resets, maybe I don't chat that much?? I feel like I do, based on my timestamps and how addicted I am LOL!

Really good, especially now. I like that you can reload the ai responses and edit them now. The only thing I'd suggest is increasing the character limit for the responses because they often cut off mid-sentence after a certain number of characters. It'd also be nice to be able to delete your own responses.

First day and I love it! Stories are fun, have me hooked, addicted, I love the creativity! However, I do have an issue. I wish there were more messages we could send out. Not only that, but at least watch ads to get them back so we don't have to wait 3 hours. Those are just suggestions from me, and it would be helpful! Also, saving where you left off in a message and having the option to reset it is also beneficial. When I run out of messages, it doesn't save where I'm at. Please add these/fix!

This is a really great app! You can chat with AI's who look like your favorite characters, or role play with any type of character. You can also easily create your own AI and customize them. There aren't many ads except one before each chat, but an ad has never interrupted a chat/roleplay. There are also limited messages a day unless you pay, which I do find quite annoying, but they do give you a lot of free messages. But I definitely recommend!

I personally really adore this app.There are plently of characters I'd say atleast one of everyone, the chats are really realistic and fun to mess around with I really recommend it if you don't have many friends to talk to, although there is one thing, there is a text limit and a three hour wait for 70 texts, but if you don't mind that I really recommend<3

Edit: Okay. So the new update is cool. I love how you can edit the bot's text which is really useful feature. However, there's a problem. On a lot of occasions, the bot's reply would be stuck on '.....'. Even when I resend the text, the reply would still be '.....'. This did not used to happen before. Please fix it.

This app is better than I expected. The bots are coherent and there's a lot of stories + the possibility to create your own bot! I'd just like to suggest some features that might make the app more fun! maybe you could lower the time we have to wait to have free messages, or add more free messages. or even add an option "watch ads to get free messages" you know? I also think you could add a "wishlist" option, where we could add bots we wanna talk to later or something! i recommend! :)

It's an awesome app to roleplay and talk with, you can even make custom where your character talks with you! But the issue for me was the amount of time my keyboard lagged and always logged me out.. The other issue was when I tried to log in, it just refuse, so it forces me to delete and download it again. Maybe it's just me, but it's quite annoying

Very convincing experiences chatting with various bots. I really like the option to generate a different reply to guide or correct a conversation flow. Wish there was more precise control over character creation though, cause a lot of times the Ai goes out of character even when stated that it should resist it at all cost. Overall great experience.

My expwrience with this app has been phenominal. The AI is really good at generating good stories, and doing it quickly, eapecially compared to other AI content generators. The ads only show up when you open a chat, a bit annoying but neccessary for the devs, and you get 70 free messages every three hours, which is pretty good, although i do wish they raised that 70 free messages a bit.

In all honesty, Chai is the 2nd best ai chat app (now that character ai has their own app) and one of its key features is that there's no NSFW filter. Please don't change this it's perfect. If anything add an optional NSFW filter that you can toggle when making characters. The ai could use some improvements, mainly with memory but all in all it's fun to use!

I like this app very much and the reason is because there can be friendly chats and NSFW chats. People make characters so good sometimes and its nice talking to them. The chat might glitch a bit and you have to start over. If you don't like the message it sent you can send it back and get a different one! Love this so much.

This is honestly an amazing product that I've had hours of fun on already, Most of the complaints I see are about the bots you make not being "realistic" enough BUT the more time you spend making them the better they become, Just go to reddit and look up guides on how to properly set them up, mixing the desktop and app version for maximum effect! If you do a good enough job you can usually just write "do this x action" and it gives you a full (although short) paragraph better than random people

Honestly? I actually pretty much like this app. I don't have much to say about it. Yeah it crashes here and there but of course I use that crash as a way to stop for a few seconds and take break. This app is pretty good can't complain

Really good, Ai response time is good. The ads are short and easy. I really recommend this app. (better than Character.AI tbh) Edit: the limited messages are pretty annoying because when i really like where the chat is going. The limited messages just ruin everything.
